Stay on this conveniently located  1BR 2 Toilet/Bath townhouse at BF Better Living village in Basak Lapu-Lapu City. It is walking distance to the Gaisano Grand Mall. Mactan Doctors Hospital is 3 mins away. Beach is 10 mins away.

It is a furnished house ideal for 2-3 persons. The (originally) 2nd bedroom upstairs  is used as a walk-in closet with a bathroom and laundry area. Cable and internet ready. Minimum rent 6 months.

Rental rate: 12,000 Pesos per month plus utilities.

For inquiries contact: +63.999.999.0993
